1050
01:30:13.158 --> 01:30:14.534
Yes.

1051
01:30:17.537 --> 01:30:19.039
So we're safe?

1052
01:30:21.166 --> 01:30:22.208
Safe.

1053
01:30:23.877 --> 01:30:25.545
Everyone is safe.

1054
01:31:32.779 --> 01:31:36.449
Eventually the Arab states
will rise against Israel.

1055
01:31:37.117 --> 01:31:40.745
They don't like Palestinians.
but they hate the Jews more.

1056
01:31:41.454 --> 01:31:43.623
It won't be like 1967.

1057
01:31:43.748 --> 01:31:47.585
The rest of the world will see
by then what the Israelis do to us.

1058
01:31:47.711 --> 01:31:51.464
They won't help when Egypt
and Syria attack. Even Jordan.

1059
01:31:52.215 --> 01:31:54.259
Israel will cease to exist.

1060
01:31:58.096 --> 01:31:59.139
