telling you what you already know.

1064
01:32:09.733 --> 01:32:12.110
You people have nothing
to bargain with.

1065
01:32:12.485 --> 01:32:14.112
You'll never get the land back.

1066
01:32:14.237 --> 01:32:17.782
You'll all die old men in
