1067
01:32:17.949 --> 01:32:20.452
We have a lot of children.
They'll have children.

1068
01:32:20.577 --> 01:32:22.037
So we can wait forever.

1069
01:32:22.120 --> 01:32:25.665
And if we need to. we can make
